1. how to run:
sudo LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/home/zxy/workspace/30Gsda5/mydpdk/dpdk-stable-25.11.1/build/lib/:/home/zxy/workspace/30Gsda5/mydpdk/dpdk-stable-25.11.1/build/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu ./build/mydpdk-shared

2. preparation:
